<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Rapport de Sécurité — {{ employe.prenom }} {{ employe.nom }}</title>
<style>
/* ========== BASE ========== */
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
body {
  font-family: 'DejaVu Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
  font-size: 10px;
  color: #1e293b;
  background: white;
  line-height: 1.45;
}

/* ========== GESTION DES SAUTS DE PAGE ========== */
.page {
  page-break-after: always;    /* chaque élément .page saute après lui */
}
.page:last-child {
  page-break-after: auto;      /* pas de saut après la dernière page */
}
.pbi {
  page-break-inside: avoid;    /* évite de couper un bloc important */
}
@page {
  margin: 1.8cm;
}

/* ========== STYLES COMMUNS ========== */
h2 {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #0f172a;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  letter-spacing: -0.2px;
}
.separator {
  height: 1px;
  background: #e2e8f0;
  margin: 12px 0;
}
.text-muted {
  color: #64748b;
  font-style: italic;
}

/* ========== PAGE DE COUVERTURE ========== */
.cover {
  background: #0f172a;
  color: white;
  padding: 2.5cm 2cm;
  position: relative;
  min-height: 27cm;
}
.cover-bar {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 6px;
  height: 100%;
  background: #1e3a8a;
}
.cover-logo {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 2cm;
}
.cover-logo-icon {
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  background: #1e3a8a;
  border-radius: 8px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 20px;
}
.cover-logo-text {
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}
.cover-logo-sub {
  font-size: 7px;
  color: #94a3b8;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  margin-top: 2px;
}
.cover-title {
  font-size: 28px;
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin: 1.2cm 0 0.3cm 0;
}
.cover-subtitle {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #94a3b8;
  margin-bottom: 1.2cm;
}
.cover-employee {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 0.2cm;
}
.cover-dept {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: #94a3b8;
  margin-bottom: 1cm;
}
.cover-meta {
  font-size: 8px;
  color: #5b6e8c;
  border-top: 1px solid #334155;
  padding-top: 10px;
  margin-top: 1.5cm;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
}
.cover-confidential {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 1.2cm;
  right: 2cm;
  font-size: 7px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  padding: 3px 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

/* ========== EN-TÊTE ET PIED DE PAGE (pages intérieures) ========== */
.header-page {
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  padding-bottom: 6px;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  font-size: 7px;
  color: #64748b;
}
.header-page strong {
  color: #0f172a;
}
.footer-page {
  border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  padding-top: 6px;
  margin-top: 18px;
  font-size: 7px;
  color: #94a3b8;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
}

/* ========== BLOCS DE CONTENU ========== */
.card {
  background: #ffffff;
  border: 1px solid #eef2f6;
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 14px 18px;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.section-title {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  color: #1e3a8a;
  border-left: 3px solid #1e3a8a;
  padding-left: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

/* Grille informations employé */
.info-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
  gap: 6px 12px;
  margin-top: 8px;
}
.info-label {
  font-size: 7.5px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #5b6e8c;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.info-value {
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: #1e293b;
}
.badge {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  font-size: 7px;
  font-weight: 700;
}
.badge-active { background: #e6f7e6; color: #166534; }
.badge-inactive { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }

/* Score avec jauge */
.score-container {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 20px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.score-circle {
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 6px solid;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
.score-circle.low    { border-color: #16a34a; color: #16a34a; background: #f0fdf4; }
.score-circle.medium { border-color: #d97706; color: #d97706; background: #fffbeb; }
.score-circle.high   { border-color: #dc2626; color: #dc2626; background: #fef2f2; }
.score-number { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; }
.score-unit   { font-size: 8px; font-weight: 500; }
.score-detail { flex: 1; }
.score-bar-label {
  font-size: 7.5px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 3px;
}
.score-bar-bg {
  height: 6px;
  background: #e2e8f0;
  border-radius: 3px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.score-bar-fill {
  height: 100%;
  border-radius: 3px;
}
.risk-pill {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 8px;
  padding: 3px 12px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  font-size: 8px;
  font-weight: 700;
}
.risk-pill.low    { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
.risk-pill.medium { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
.risk-pill.high   { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }

/* Cartes d'indicateurs */
.stats-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.stat-box {
  flex: 1;
  text-align: center;
  background: #f8fafc;
  border: 1px solid #eef2f6;
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 10px 6px;
}
.stat-number {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #0f172a;
  line-height: 1;
}
.stat-label {
  font-size: 7px;
  color: #64748b;
  margin-top: 4px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* Listes d'analyse / recommandations */
.analysis-list, .reco-list {
  border-left: 3px solid #1e3a8a;
  background: #ffffff;
  padding: 8px 0 8px 12px;
}
.analysis-item, .reco-item {
  display: flex;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  font-size: 9px;
  line-height: 1.4;
}
.analysis-dot {
  width: 5px;
  height: 5px;
  background: #1e3a8a;
  border-radius: 50%;
  margin-top: 5px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.reco-num {
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  background: #1e3a8a;
  color: white;
  border-radius: 18px;
  font-size: 8px;
  font-weight: 700;
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 1px;
}

/* Tableau des formations */
.formation-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  font-size: 8.5px;
}
.formation-table th {
  text-align: left;
  padding: 8px 4px;
  background: #f1f5f9;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #1e293b;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
}
.formation-table td {
  padding: 8px 4px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
  vertical-align: middle;
}
.progress {
  width: 80px;
  height: 5px;
  background: #e2e8f0;
  border-radius: 3px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.progress-fill {
  height: 100%;
  background: #1e3a8a;
}

/* Bloc risque */
.risk-block {
  background: #f9fafb;
  border: 1px solid #eef2f6;
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 14px 18px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
}
.risk-icon {
  font-size: 32px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.risk-title {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 800;
}
.risk-desc {
  font-size: 8.5px;
  color: #475569;
  margin-top: 2px;
}

/* Conclusion */
.conclusion {
  background: #fcfcfd;
  border-left: 3px solid #1e3a8a;
  padding: 12px 16px;
  font-size: 9px;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.conclusion-footer {
  margin-top: 10px;
  font-size: 7px;
  color: #7c8ba0;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
}

/* Mention éthique */
.ethics {
  background: #f9fafb;
  border: 1px solid #eef2f6;
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  display: flex;
  gap: 10px;
}
.ethics-icon {
  font-size: 18px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.ethics-text {
  font-size: 7.5px;
  color: #475569;
}
.ethics-title {
  font-size: 8px;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 2px;
}

.empty {
  text-align: center;
  color: #94a3b8;
  padding: 12px;
  font-size: 8px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

{# ---------------- PAGE 1 : COUVERTURE ---------------- #}
<div class="page cover">
  <div class="cover-bar"></div>
  <div class="cover-logo">
    
    <div>
      <div class="cover-logo-text">SAT Platform</div>
      <div class="cover-logo-sub">Security Awareness Training</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cover-title">Rapport individuel</div>
  <div class="cover-subtitle">Évaluation de la vigilance cybersécurité</div>
  <div class="cover-employee">{{ employe.prenom }} {{ employe.nom }}</div>
  <div class="cover-dept">{{ employe.departement ? employe.departement.nom : 'Département non assigné' }}</div>
  <div class="cover-meta">
    <span>Réf. : RPT-{{ employe.id }}-{{ "now"|date("Ymd") }}</span>
    <span>Émis le : {{ "now"|date("d/m/Y") }}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cover-confidential">CONFIDENTIEL · Usage interne</div>
</div>

{# ---------------- PAGE 2 : INFORMATIONS & SCORE ---------------- #}
<div class="page">
  <div class="header-page">
    <span><strong>{{ employe.prenom }} {{ employe.nom }}</strong> — Rapport de vigilance</span>
    <span>Page 1 / 3</span>
  </div>

  {# Section 1 : Informations générales #}
  <div class="card pbi">
    <div class="section-title">1. Informations générales</div>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start;">
      <div style="width: 48px; height: 48px; background: #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 800; font-size: 18px;">
        {{ employe.prenom|slice(0,1)|upper }}{{ employe.nom|slice(0,1)|upper }}
      </div>
      <div class="info-grid" style="flex:1;">
        <span class="info-label">Email</span><span class="info-value">{{ employe.email }}</span>
        <span class="info-label">Département</span><span class="info-value">{{ employe.departement ? employe.departement.nom : 'Non assigné' }}</span>
        <span class="info-label">Poste</span><span class="info-value">{{ employe.poste ?? 'Non renseigné' }}</span>
        <span class="info-label">Statut</span><span class="info-value">{% if employe.estActif %}<span class="badge badge-active">Actif</span>{% else %}<span class="badge badge-inactive">Inactif</span>{% endif %}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {# Section 2 : Score global #}
  <div class="card pbi">
    <div class="section-title">2. Score global de vigilance</div>
    {% set riskClass = niveauRisque == 'faible' ? 'low' : (niveauRisque == 'moyen' ? 'medium' : 'high') %}
    <div class="score-container">
      <div class="score-circle {{ riskClass }}">
        <span class="score-number">{{ scoreVigilance|round }}</span>
        <span class="score-unit">/100</span>
      </div>
      <div class="score-detail">
        <div class="score-bar-label">
          <span>Score de vigilance</span>
          <span>{{ scoreVigilance|round }}%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="score-bar-bg">
          <div class="score-bar-fill {{ riskClass }}" style="width: {{ scoreVigilance }}%;"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="risk-pill {{ riskClass }}">Niveau : {{ niveauRisque|capitalize }}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {# Section 3 : Indicateurs clés #}
  <div class="card pbi">
    <div class="section-title">3. Indicateurs comportementaux</div>
    <div class="stats-row">
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-number">{{ nbEnvoyes }}</div><div class="stat-label">Campagnes reçues</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-number">{{ nbClics }}</div><div class="stat-label">Clics suspects</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-number">{{ nbSignalements }}</div><div class="stat-label">Signalements</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-number">{{ formationsTerminees }}</div><div class="stat-label">Modules validés</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {# Section 4 : Analyse #}
  <div class="card pbi">
    <div class="section-title">4. Analyse comportementale</div>
    <div class="analysis-list">
      <div class="analysis-item"><span class="analysis-dot"></span><span>Reçu <strong>{{ nbEnvoyes }}</strong> simulations de phishing.</span></div>
      <div class="analysis-item"><span class="analysis-dot"></span><span>Clic sur <strong>{{ nbClics }}</strong> lien(s) suspect(s) → <strong>{{ clickRate }}%</strong> de clics.</span></div>
      <div class="analysis-item"><span class="analysis-dot"></span><span>Signalement de <strong>{{ nbSignalements }}</strong> emails → taux <strong>{{ reportRate }}%</strong>.</span></div>
      <div class="analysis-item"><span class="analysis-dot"></span><span>Formations suivies : <strong>{{ formationsTerminees }}</strong> module(s) terminé(s).</span></div>
      {% if clickRate > 20 %}
      <div class="analysis-item"><span class="analysis-dot"></span><span><strong>Attention :</strong> taux de clic élevé. Une sensibilisation renforcée est conseillée.</span></div>
      {% endif %}
      {% if reportRate < 20 %}
      <div class="analysis-item"><span class="analysis-dot"></span><span><strong>Marge de progression :</strong> le réflexe de signalement peut être amélioré.</span></div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-page">
    <span>SAT Platform — Rapport confidentiel</span>
    <span>Généré le {{ dateRapport|split(' à ')|first }}</span>
  </div>
</div>

{# ---------------- PAGE 3 : RECOMMANDATIONS, FORMATIONS, RISQUE, CONCLUSION ---------------- #}
<div class="page">
  <div class="header-page">
    <span><strong>{{ employe.prenom }} {{ employe.nom }}</strong> — Rapport de vigilance</span>
    <span>Page 2 / 3</span>
  </div>

  {# Section 5 : Recommandations #}
  <div class="card pbi">
    <div class="section-title">5. Recommandations personnalisées</div>
    <div class="reco-list">
      {% set rec_num = 1 %}
      {% if clickRate > 20 %}
      <div class="reco-item"><span class="reco-num">{{ rec_num }}</span><span>Suivre une formation complémentaire sur la détection des faux emails.</span></div>
      {% set rec_num = rec_num + 1 %}
      {% endif %}
      <div class="reco-item"><span class="reco-num">{{ rec_num }}</span><span>Participer aux prochaines campagnes de phishing pour entretenir sa vigilance.</span></div>
      {% set rec_num = rec_num + 1 %}
      <div class="reco-item"><span class="reco-num">{{ rec_num }}</span><span>Signaler systématiquement tout email suspect via le bouton dédié.</span></div>
      {% if formationsTerminees < 2 %}
      {% set rec_num = rec_num + 1 %}
      <div class="reco-item"><span class="reco-num">{{ rec_num }}</span><span>Terminer les modules de formation recommandés sur la plateforme.</span></div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>

  {# Section 6 : Historique des formations #}
  <div class="card pbi">
    <div class="section-title">6. Historique des formations</div>
    {% if progressions|length > 0 %}
    <table class="formation-table">
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Module</th><th>Statut</th><th>Progression</th><th>Date fin</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for prog in progressions %}
        <tr>
          <td><strong>{{ prog.module ? prog.module.titre : 'Module' }}</strong></td>
          <td>
            {% if prog.statut == 'TERMINE' %} Terminé
            {% elseif prog.statut == 'EN_COURS' %} En cours
            {% else %} Non commencé{% endif %}
          </td>
          <td>
            <div class="progress"><div class="progress-fill" style="width: {{ prog.pourcentageProgression }}%;"></div></div>
            <span style="font-size:7px;">{{ prog.pourcentageProgression }}%</span>
          </td>
          <td>{{ prog.dateTermine ? prog.dateTermine|date('d/m/Y') : '—' }}</td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
    {% else %}
    <div class="empty">Aucune formation enregistrée.</div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>

  {# Section 7 : Niveau de risque #}
  <div class="card pbi">
    <div class="section-title">7. Niveau de risque cyber</div>
    <div class="risk-block">
      <div class="risk-icon">{% if niveauRisque == 'faible' %}🟢{% elseif niveauRisque == 'moyen' %}🟠{% else %}🔴{% endif %}</div>
      <div>
        <div class="risk-title">{{ niveauRisque|capitalize }}</div>
        <div class="risk-desc">
          {% if niveauRisque == 'faible' %}
            Score ≥ 60/100. Comportements sécuritaires satisfaisants.
          {% elseif niveauRisque == 'moyen' %}
            Score entre 35 et 59/100. Des améliorations sont attendues.
          {% else %}
            Score < 35/100. Risque élevé, action corrective nécessaire.
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-page">
    <span>SAT Platform — Rapport confidentiel</span>
    <span>Généré le {{ dateRapport|split(' à ')|first }}</span>
  </div>
</div>

{# ---------------- PAGE 4 : CONCLUSION & MENTIONS ---------------- #}
<div class="page">
  <div class="header-page">
    <span><strong>{{ employe.prenom }} {{ employe.nom }}</strong>  Rapport de vigilance</span>
    <span>Page 3 / 3</span>
  </div>

  <div class="card pbi">
    <div class="section-title">8. Conclusion</div>
    <div class="conclusion">
      {{ niveauRisque == 'faible' ? "L'employé démontre de bonnes pratiques de sécurité. Il est recommandé de maintenir cette dynamique par des piqûres de rappel régulières." : (niveauRisque == 'moyen' ? "Une vigilance moyenne est observée. Des actions de sensibilisation ciblées (formation, simulations) sont conseillées pour réduire les risques." : "Le niveau de vigilance est critique. Un plan d'action personnalisé doit être mis en place immédiatement.") }}
      <div class="conclusion-footer">
        <span>SAT Platform – génération automatique</span>
        <span>{{ dateRapport }}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card pbi">
    <div class="section-title">9. Mention éthique et légale</div>
    <div class="ethics">
      <div class="ethics-icon">⚖️</div>
      <div class="ethics-text">
        <div class="ethics-title">Conformité et confidentialité</div>
        Aucune donnée sensible (mot de passe, information personnelle confidentielle) n'a été collectée. Ce rapport est destiné à un usage interne exclusif. Il ne peut être communiqué à des tiers sans autorisation explicite du RSSI. Conforme aux recommandations ANSSI et ISO 27001.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-page">
    <span>Document confidentiel — Usage interne</span>
    <span>Réf. RPT-{{ employe.id }}-{{ "now"|date("Ymd") }}</span>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>